I was going to post this as a reply on DA, but people are stupid, and I don't need mindless flak from brainless assholes.

     A whole hell of a lot of people have the wrong ideas about what happened at columbine 5 years ago today.  For one thing, they, at least Eric, didn't do it because they were bullied.  Another thing is that Eric was a genius, and not ignorant.  Eric had an unbelievably large hate for ignorance itself.  If you ever read parts of the journal that Eric kept, you would agree with me.  He saw most everybody in the world as inferior, and he didn't plan this for the school because of the students or teachers harassing him.  He just saw it as the best place to put a dent in history, as the students and faculty in the school were in close proximity to each other, and many could easily be killed by bombs, and many fleeing survivors could be shot.  Eric was a blatant psychopath, and despite what anybody may think, Eric could NEVER have been helped.  His death at columbine may have saved the lives of thousands.  Eric was more calm and calculating, and just plain de-sensitized than anybody (who is not a psychopath) could comprehend.  Dylan, on the other hand, was angry at himself for his problems.  He was a real loose cannon, homicidal, and suicidal.  
Out of the two, Dylan could have been helped.  If it weren't for Eric's plans, Dylan would probably never have exploded like he did at columbine.  
Some people don't understand that this could have been so much worse.  If Eric's master plan for the school succeeded, and if their bombs had been wired correctly, a total of about 600 or 700 deaths to faculty, students, reporters, police, and residents of the area would have been easily attained.  In short, Eric wanted to kill as many people as humanly possible.  He exclaimed on one of his videos that he was going to dwarf the Oklahoma City bombing, and that he was going to go down in history as the mastermind behind the mass killings in columbine.  Dylan did not need to die, but Eric's death probably in the end did save many, many lives.  If he had not perished, and had not columbine been the target, every year of his life would have been dedicated to planning the biggest killing by one man in history.  
In the end, this really should not have happened.  People should have seen this coming, and people should have noticed the smaller things, such as the trench coat mafia, and taken steps to stop Eric and Dylan before this happened.  It really is sad, but at least the shooting didn't happen the way it was 'supposed' to.


I left out alot of what I wanted to say, and I left out a few other things that I didn't think people would understand.  

Besides, who the fuck reads my journal anyways?

I rolled over out of my bed and onto a bar coming out of my chair, cracking my spine, which was fun when I look back at it.  I pranced downstairs like a giddy little girl ready for another day of pretending to learn shit while I sleep and doodle.  I draw lots of stuff but it never makes it's way to DA because I can't ink worth shit and it makes me cry.   Anyways, yeah!  I compare my work too much to others, or at least some people say so. I honestly feel like throwing myself onto a live grenade right now just to see how far my body parts would scatter.  Dogdammit I'm cynical.

It seems the world is against me this week, including the weather.  It's been rainy and cold all week and I'm sick of it.  I want snow.  Snow is fun.  I guess I can't blame the weather on myself, but everything else, I can.

It's not so much one or two big things gone wrone.  It's one or two big things AND a bunch of small things.  At least I'm a bit more composed than yesterday.  I was a total wreck.  I actually cried yesterday.  I can't remember the last time I cried in depression.  My paranoia is emphasizing all of it too.  I think they are going to up my dosage of Paxil officially now.  I don't blame them, but I still hate the fact that I depend on pills to keep me going.  If I don't take it for a day, I get headaches, I almost pass out, and I can't focus on anything.  I just feel like sleeping all day.

UMD probably will give me shit for my class rank, which is apparently in the 20 or 30% range, but I have never gotten a grade in high school lower than a C-.  It baffles me that more than 80 percent of my dumbass school can get all A's and B's.  I've actually been good last year too.  I didn't get anything lower than a B- last year, and same for this year, but that doesn't matter because colleges don't look at senior grades.  Bah.  Damn it all.

I gotta rest for awhile.  I've been sleepy today.  I'll probably babble more later.

I feel horrible

I can't even talk about it now.

Haven't eaten since early monday.

I did it all to myself

Nobody brought this upon me

Part of me saw it coming

Larger part blocked it away

Cant focus on anything

Completely fucked up

I feel horrible

Gwah...  I'm back in school tomrorrow after a 5 day weekend for MEA... whatever the hell that is.  I don't give a shanty about what it is.. I just care that I get a long weekend!  Woohoo!  School starts tomorrow at about noon, and that's a pretty late start.  Rock on.

Today was just like every other day this weekend.  I hanged out with friends all day and did the same stuff I have been doing for the past 5 days.  We went to Davannis, watched Jeremy and Betsy make out, played a little classic nintendo, and drove around doing really stupid things.  I just wish my friends were a little more like me.  I have to act different around my friends, and I hate it.  If I say what I want, and do what I want, people don't talk to me.  I wish so much that I didn't care, but I do, and I hate it.

Urg...  I really don't want to go to school tomorrow.  School sucks, but at least it's a short day.  If this was a full week, I would have to freak out and fake a nervous breakdown to try and get out of school for a bit.  Ryan got expelled a few days ago... lucky bastard.  Well, not so lucky I guess.  It all happened when Ryan started letting his friends draw/write on him in theatre class, and one of them wrote 'must kill all teachers', and since now all of the sudden after columbine, american society takes every single little detail so literally.  Some dumbass sees the writing on his arm and fucking reports him, and the principal actually orders Ryans car to be searched in the parking lot.  Now, Ryan has had a dinky pellet gun in his trunk for almost 2 years, and nobody cared.  Nobody cared because the fucking thing can't peirce skin, and has about the same chance of killing somebody as a sloth in a deep coma.  They saw the pellet gun in his car, and oh my fuckin god he is going to shoot up the school!  Jeez... they even say that they just want to make an example of Ryan to other kids in my school.  They feel that putting a little control and fear into students is worth ruining a life.  Ryan isn't having a good time with this.  Everything is fucking up for him, and most of his plans for graduation and college have been destroyed just because one principal wanted to make an example.  Ryan isn't the kind of kid who would run into school with a gun and shoot everybody.  Gaaaah...  most people suck you know?  Especially normal people. =P

Bah...  time to log on and talk to teh wuffie!  Buhbai.

Friends came and went today.  Three of them if you give a shit.  Jeremy, Ryan, and Betsy were over today for more than a few hours.  Don't get me wrong, I don't care if they are over here or not, but there is something about everything.  It makes no sence 'something about everything', but in my mind it does, and I have no clue how to explain it.  It's like every single thought and word that comes around means so many things, and you can never tell what exactly somebody means.  It all just makes me want to drive away to some corn field and dissapear for days, or forever.  Gah...   I didn't even come close to saying what I mean, so pay no attention to what I just said..  

Ryan had to go to work at about 4PM, then it was just Jeremy, Betsy, and the invisible third wheel.  You can take a wild stab at the not so secret identity of him.  Wow, it's me.  Anyways, I'm invisible in my house.  I'm not insane yet... I mean invisible as in nobody even cares I'm there, and I don't know how to explain it, but I'm glad they don't care.  Here is a little example.  Betsy broke up with her boyfriend a few weeks ago, and now she has my best friend Jeremy.  Anyways, they start getting all riled up, and it goes from a little kiss, to full on.. whatever you wish to call it.  No, not really sex I guess given which part of the body in which organ, but still pretty damn close.  At all times, I was no more than 10 feet away, either reading, watching tv, or commiting genocide on Dynasty Warriors 4 (love that game).  They must have had a total of 4 or 5 ejaculations on one couch.  I'm not even going to talk about the condition of the couch, but that's beside the point.  They just don't care that I'm there, and they don't acknolege me in my own home.  It's almost like they come over almost every day to just talk about how much they love fucking, and finger eachother silly.  Don't get pissed if you know who I'm talking about, or you are who I'm talking about, because I'm not trying to get you mad or anything.  I'm just being a cynical bitch, and I like it.

I love being ignored, hated, feared, and above all.. not understood.
I can't explain why, but I just do.  My biggest fear in this fucking world is being normal.  I hate being like everybody else.  This is all inside me though.  I can't bring who I am out to the world all at one time.  I may dress and act a little strange, but I wish I could really just let go of society.  I still have a small instict to be accepted by the majority of humans, and it makes me want to vomit.

Since I never act the way I do on the inside, all my friends, and all who know me, are normal.  I hate normal people.  I want to know freaks who can actually give me a hand at setting society aflame....  damn normals.

I feel really pissed in general right now, and I don't know why.

What is this???  I'm updating this thing?  Wow...

Hey, ya know, lots of stuff happened between now and my last serious update, but I'm a lazy bunny and I won't even think about talking about any of it!  Anyways, here is a summary...

Good stuff happened
Bad stuff happened
Ugly stuff happened

Yeah, some summary huh?  You are probably saying to yourself "WHATTHEFUCKISWRONGWITHTHISFUCKINGLAPINEWHOTHEHELLTOOKMYSOUPWHERESMYKEYSDAMMITDAMMITDAMMIT", but I don't care.

I think I may be updating about my actual life sometimes, and that's saying that I actually have one, which I DO NOT!  Ahem, anyways, I went to THE MARILYN MANSON CONCERT!!!  He was less than 30 feet away from me and I think I spunked my shorts.  He is the one person in this dumbass world who has come close to inspiring me as much as the wuffie has.  Oh, by the way, during the concerts and between the fights, manson dropped a huge amount of rose confetti on the crowd, and I picked some up to send to teh wuffie!  I'm so proud that I got a souviner for my mostest favrote wruffskie in teh whoel fcuking woreld! ^.^ ...  fuck spelling.  

Manson was talking about lots of shit, and I loved every second of it!
"If God lived on earth... I would BREAK his fucking windowsss...
If God was a woman... I would fuck her *finger* in the assss...
If god was black...  I would be the white fucking satan
If god was a lie... then ROCK... IS... DEAD"
They played Rock Is Dead right after that, and it ruled.

He also stated that minnesota is a good place to be, just not in prison.  As some of you may know, he had a court case in st paul (50 miles away from me) a few weeks ago after plopping his balls on a security guards head...  I love manson ^.^
He won by the way!  Huzzah!

Friends here!  Done writing... more later!

Pssssh... who wants to be normal anyways? Today sucked. I think it even teetered on the edge of blowing too. First off, I haven't been getting much sleep at all for the past few days, and with it being the first week of school, the stress level is certainly up just a bit. I usually fall asleep at about 3:30 in the morning, and I have to get up about 4 hours later. I feel so so messed up right now. It feels like everything in life contradicts everything else. I think too deeply into things.. it's like shoving my head into a blender. The first few inches are fine, but whats this? A spinning metal thi.. *BWWWWWWRRRRIIIIISSSSSSHHHHHHHHHHHH* I can't beleive how fucked up society is today. I want NOTHING to do with any of it. I can't even explain why it's so fucked up, because I have no clue where to start. It would take me days to just write down a quarter of what I want to say. Gaaaah... I need to calm down, but is isn't that easy anymore. Shit happens that I can't get over, because right when I start to feel okay, I get hit with something else. I keep telling myself that I will figure life out and get through everything, but just trying to understand why I'm telling myself gives me a headache. I feel like that everybody is passing me while I stand alone trying to figure out why I'm here doing the things I do, and why everybody else goes around thinking the way they do. I'm sure that nobody reading this is following me, so I'll just stop... Gaaaaaah... I got pulled over today! Yes, I was speeding, and I was too busy thinking about other things to care, but wait, there's more! It all happened when I was trying to follow ryan (who friggin does 50 on 30mph roads) to the grocery store so we (Mike, Ryan, John, and I) could get chinese food. So I'm doing 42 to follow ryan, and this white car pulls up behind me with these little red flashy lights inside the cabin. I thought it was some moron trying to piss me off at first, but then I saw the badge! I then pulled over to let him by, because I was assuming he was going to stop ryan for going about 50 through a stop sign, but NO!!! HE STOPS ME!!! I pull over and this cop follows me to the curb. He gets out while I bash my head into the steering wheel just to try and figure out how the fuck this happened! He gets to my window and asks for my drivers license, and tells me I was going 42 through a 30mph zone, but RYAN... was going at least 10mph faster while he was trying to 'lose' me. Of course I didn't point out the cop's stupidity, because he would probably throw his gun at me to give him the right to pull me out of my car and stomp my face into the pavement. Oh I can just see it now! Cop: Liscense please. Me: GAAAAAH WHATTHEFUCKAREYOUSTOPPINGMEFORGODDAMMITYOUFUCKINGMORONICPEICEOFSHI... Cop: *'drops' his gun into the drivers lap* He's got a gun!!! Me: What?!?! Cop: *pulls the teenage ass-wipe out of his car and beats the living piss out of him* Me: Goes to court and loses because society is fucked up. Maybe I'm over-reacting, and I'm greatful that the cop only gave me a warning, but still... Shouldn't they have under-cover cops doing better things than catching speeders? Aren't there murders, gangs, and drug-cartels operating all around you? Why no! Just a dumb kid speeding. Oh my god stop him! Pfffft... I'm going to stop rambling now. Also... There is somebody I miss more than my sanity right now. I at least got to talk to him for a few minutes today, but he was having a really bad couple of days. I tried to do my best to help him, but there is so little I can do. I want to be there with him, but it's just so hard to talk to my parents... I have to tell them so many things to get them to help me plan this trip to see him and buy me a ticket maybe... I need to get over it. It's still so hard. I just want to be next to him, but I don't know how long it will take. I know that someday I will find myself at his door, but there are so many variables that could make or break everything. I also have to admit that it hurts to think about him and talk about him. I can't even explain why. It's just that I feel so insignificant in life.. I can't get deeper into this..
